# 🚀 NOTES (IMPORTANT FOR FUTURE YOU)

## ⚠️ Why metrics can look very high:

* rule-based target construction
* high-dimensional dummy features
* strong structural patterns in survey data

---

## ⚠️ Common risk points:

* feature explosion after dummy encoding
* rare category instability
* implicit proxy leakage from survey variables

